{"tid":1066301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【維和任務】中國提議加入「一帶一路」字眼 美怒斥：不顧他國人民死活","createTime":"2019-03-17T23:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T05:22:37.000Z","uid":141151,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"273cf1dc8328fe4e62dc1eab4ad8ad718d1816c8","tid":1066301,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T23:49:27.000Z","msg":"【維和任務】中國提議加入「一帶一路」字眼 美怒斥：不顧他國人民死活<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190317/59377621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59377621&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=9bc01f7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190317%2F59377621&h=32aeafc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190317/59377621</a><br />\n<br />\n美國駐聯合國副代表科恩（Jonathan Cohen）於當地時間周五（15日）在聯合國安理會上，與中國駐聯合國副代表吳海濤，就中國提倡的「一帶一路」激烈交鋒。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">安理會當日原定討論延長阿富汗維和任務1年的議案，但中國要求於議案內加入「一帶一路」的字眼，遭到美國反對。科恩表示，「一帶一路」與阿富汗的維和任務，沒甚麼太大的關係，且「一帶一路」欠缺透明、弊案叢生，導致不少國家出現貪污、巨額負債、環境被破壞。他又指，中國想綁架安理會議案，一切以自國的政治為優先，而並不以阿富汗人民的福祉為主要考慮。</span><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">吳海濤駁斥，「一帶一路」旨在實現共同發展和繁榮的經濟合作，與地緣政治無關，認為科恩的言論充滿偏見、扭曲事實。他又強調，至今已有超國123個國家與中國簽署合作協議。但對於科恩指出，「一帶一路」令多國背上巨債，吳海濤則避談。</span><br />\n<br />\n在中國的堅持、美國不讓步的情況下，安理會最後只好採納臨時過渡方案，將聯合國維和部隊派駐阿富汗的時間從1年減少至6個月。草擬議案的德國駐聯合國大使厄斯根（Christoph Heusgen）對於這樣的結果感到遺憾，批評中國對「一帶一路」的堅持，根本與維和任務毫無關係。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"8b750889aa7a8061fca76d9b498c93fb017aba7f","tid":1066301,"uid":84926,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:00:27.000Z","msg":"咁撚中意認叻<br />\n港鐵炒車仲唔係關一帶一路事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f8148abf5cd323f559ff344bc3801258374ef2","tid":1066301,"uid":57376,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:09:48.000Z","msg":"癡鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都關一帶死路事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新萬能key<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f105515d8ecd762a2a21c90ad938a794d3d179","tid":1066301,"uid":33907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"睇嚟支那已經覺得侵侵連唔到任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff9d0101676a43523cb32a330948f89b69ec6b2","tid":1066301,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T00:34:40.000Z","msg":"癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4994683e61f985da769bef3be7e1cfeea896bbd","tid":1066301,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"大中亞共榮圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a09c3811418a63983b0eb29435b75e2a2b5aec","tid":1066301,"uid":75326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:31:28.000Z","msg":"中國擺明響安理會玩嘢<br />\n聯合國根本就係冇機制阻止"},{"pid":"47ca0c24c8ac2396ecefdab8623782ff230c1e29","tid":1066301,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>草擬議案的德國駐聯合國大使厄斯根（Christoph Heusgen）對於這樣的結果感到遺憾，批評中國對「一帶一路」的堅持，根本與維和任務毫無關係。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n支那狗真係CLS"},{"pid":"0aede2ac765d3407b1d00b8d25c911753bf4a3bc","tid":1066301,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T04:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一帶一路維和部隊"},{"pid":"349454a629dca22afb4beb46c22564b423c189d6","tid":1066301,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}